article_title: Obamacare Fuels Surprising Jump In Hospital Admissions

article_metadata.description: The Affordable Care Act is increasing hospital admissions, which had been flat or falling for several years before the law expanded coverage to millions of Americans.
article_metadata.author: Bruce Japsen
